test:
  commands:
    - python -c "import numpy; numpy.show_config()"
    - python -c "import scipy, sys; sys.exit(not scipy.test(verbose=1, label='full',
      tests=None, extra_argv=['-k', 'not (_not_a_real_test or test_x0_equals_Mb[bicgstab)',
      '-nauto', '--timeout=1200', '--durations=50']))"
  requires:
    - mpmath
    - pooch
    - pytest
    - pytest-timeout
    - pytest-xdist
